        {
          "rule": "Numbers 1-10 in Darija",
          "explanation": "Darija numbers differ significantly from MSA. The sequence is: wa7d, jouj, tlata, rb3a, khmsa, stta, sb3a, tmnya, ts3ud, 3shra.",
          "examples": [
            {
              "arabic": "واحد، جوج، تلاتة، ربعة، خمسة",
